
  EPA STORM WATER MANAGEMENT MODEL - VERSION 5.2 (Build 5.2.4)
  ------------------------------------------------------------

  Demonstrates the fix for a v5.1.013 bug that ignored soil moisture deficit recovery for Green-Ampt exfiltration 
  from storage units. Running this data set shows that for second storm event the storage unit using G-A exfiltration 
  correctly empties at same rate as after the first event since moisture deficit has fully recovered. 
  
